OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F435A1784220475
OL,3,CWelsh Government lose supplementary
OL,4,CBudget vote
OL,6,FThe Welsh Government has faced a loss
OL,7,Fin a vote on its latest spending plans
OL,8,Fin which they were defeated by 49
OL,9,Fvotes to 44.
OL,11,FSenedd members held a debate and voted
OL,12,Fon the spending proposals. However,
OL,13,Fthe Plaid Cymru government did not
OL,14,Fgain enough votes to pass the budget.
OL,16,FReform UK Wales and the Welsh
OL,17,FConservatives restated their decision
OL,18,Fnot to back it while Labour has
OL,19,Fpublicly described the offer as 'not
OL,20,Fenough.'
OL,1,Wj5hw}j5 ~shws                   G1/10
